Lineplot

In[9]:
tmp_df = df_accom[["YrSold", "YearBuilt", "SalePrice"]]

tmp_x = []
tmp_y = []

i_year = 1900
while i_year < tmp_df["YearBuilt"].max() + 10:

    if i_year == 1900:
        tmp_y.append(
            tmp_df[tmp_df["YearBuilt"] < i_year].agg({"SalePrice": "mean"}).values[0]
        )
    else:
        tmp_y.append(
            tmp_df[
                (tmp_df["YearBuilt"] >= i_year - 10) & (tmp_df["YearBuilt"] < i_year)
            ]
            .agg({"SalePrice": "mean"})
            .values[0]
        )

    tmp_x.append(i_year)

    i_year += 10

text_for_lineplot = f"""
  ,      
  , ..     , 
  .

  1900 ,   
 , ,   
 ,      90 .
"""

plot_info = {
    "title": "       ",
    "xlabel": " ",
    "ylabel": " ( $ USA)",
    "text": text_for_lineplot,
}

fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 7))  # , dpi=500)


ax.plot(tmp_x, tmp_y, marker="o", color=custom_pallete["orange"])
ax.set(
    title=plot_info["title"],
    xlabel=plot_info["xlabel"],
    ylabel=plot_info["ylabel"],
    xticks=tmp_x,
    xlim=(1895, 2015),
)
tmp_x = [f"{tmp_x[i] - 10}-{tmp_x[i]-1}" for i in range(len(tmp_x))]
tmp_x[0] = "< 1900"
tmp_x[-1] = "> 2000"
ax.axes.set_xticklabels(tmp_x, rotation=45)

ax.annotate(
    plot_info["text"],
    xy=(1910, 2.0e5),
    bbox=dict(boxstyle="square", fc="w", alpha=0.7),
    fontsize=12,
    alpha=1,
)

pdf.savefig(bbox_inches = 'tight')
# plt.show()

text_for_pieplot = f"""
  
 : 
    - Pconc
    - CBlock
"""

plot_info = {
    "title": "  ()",
    "xlabel": "",
    "ylabel": "",
    "text": text_for_pieplot,
}


tmp_x = df_accom["Foundation"].value_counts()

x = tmp_x[:4].values
x[3] = tmp_x[3:-1].values.sum()

labels = df_accom["Foundation"].value_counts().index.values[:4]
labels[3] = f"Else: { df_accom['Foundation'].value_counts().index.values[3:] }"


fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 7))  # , dpi=500)


ax.pie(
    x=x, 
    labels=labels,
    autopct='%1.1f%%',
)

ax.set(
    title=plot_info["title"],
)

ax.annotate(
    plot_info["text"],
    xy=(1, 0.5),
    bbox=dict(boxstyle="square", fc="w", alpha=0.7),
    fontsize=12,
    alpha=1,
)

pdf.savefig(bbox_inches = 'tight')
